    "body": "PartitionReaderWithBytesRead is incrementing task bytes read by the result of the callback produced by getFSBytesReadOnThreadCallback, but that callback is probably returning the _total_ bytes read, not the bytes read since the last invocation.  That means we're probably over-counting bytes if the same PartitionReaderWithBytesRead instance produces more than one batch.",
